=== 評價 ===
該片獲得多數影評人的好評。[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的159篇專業影評文章中，有122篇給予該片「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為76%，平均得分6.4分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/goosebumps_2015/ | title=Goosebumps | work=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher={{link-en|Flixster|Flixster}} | accessdate=2016-04-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502055914/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/goosebumps_2015 | archive-date=2016-05-02 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，而基於另一影評匯總網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的29篇評論文章，其中15篇予以好評，1篇差評，13篇褒貶不一，平均分為60（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/goosebumps | title=Goosebumps reviews | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=2016-02-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305181354/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/goosebumps | archive-date=2016-03-05 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「A」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/goosebumps-bridge-of-spies-crimson-peak-weekend-box-office-1201585023/ |title=‘Goosebumps’ Raises Hair At The B.O., While ‘Crimson Peak’s Recedes |work=deadline.com |access-date=2015-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018155251/http://deadline.com/2015/10/goosebumps-bridge-of-spies-crimson-peak-weekend-box-office-1201585023/ |archive-date=2015-10-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
《怪物遊戲》在北美共進帳8,010萬美元，其他地區7,010萬美元，全球總計1.502億美元，而其製片預算為5,800萬美元<ref name=BOM />。

在美國及加拿大，據推測，電影將於首週末於3,501家劇院發行，票房約位在2,000萬至3,100萬美元之間。然而，索尼更為保守，估計該片於首週末的票房收入為1,200萬至1,500萬美元<ref name="proj">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/goosebumps-crimson-peak-bridge-of-spies-steven-spielberg-the-martian-box-office-1201581325/|title=‘Goosebumps’ Set To Freak Out, But ‘The Martian’ Could Scare It Away – Box Office Preview|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2015-10-14|accessdate=2015-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015132011/http://deadline.com/2015/10/goosebumps-crimson-peak-bridge-of-spies-steven-spielberg-the-martian-box-office-1201581325/|archive-date=2015-10-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4113|title=Forecast: 'Goosebumps', 'Spies' & 'Crimson Peak' Jostle for Audience Attention|author=Brad Brevet|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|date=2015-10-15|accessdate=2015-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018171114/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4113|archive-date=2015-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Thursday">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-crimson-peak-creeps-832523|title=Box Office: 'Crimson Peak' Creeps to $855K, 'Goosebumps' Raises $600K Thursday Night|author=Rebecca Ford|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2015-10-16|accessdate=2015-10-16}}</ref>。《怪物遊戲》於2015年10月16日和《[[間諜橋|間諜橋]]》、《[[腥紅山莊|腥紅山莊]]》及《{{link-en|橄欖球傳奇|Woodlawn (film)}}》一同上映，票房專家指出，除了上映第三週的《[[絕地救援|絕地救援]]》之外，電影並沒有面臨激烈的競爭<ref name="boxoffice"/>。在其首映週末，電影進帳2,350萬美元，超越工作室預測，並位居當週票房冠軍。該成績使其成為索尼第四部在首週獲得冠軍的秋季電影。先前，工作室在過去七個星期共有三部電影達成：《[[戰爭房間|戰爭房間]]》、《[[完美傢伙|完美傢伙]]》和《[[尖叫旅社2|尖叫旅社2]]》<ref name="GB">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/goosebumps-bridge-of-spies-crimson-peak-weekend-box-office-1201585023/|title=‘Goosebumps’ Raises Hair With $23.5M, ‘Bridge Of Spies’ Eyes $15.4M; ‘Crimson Peak’ Ekes Out $12.8M – Sunday Postmortem|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2015-10-18|accessdate=2015-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018155251/http://deadline.com/2015/10/goosebumps-bridge-of-spies-crimson-peak-weekend-box-office-1201585023/|archive-date=2015-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4114&p=.htm|title='Goosebumps' On Top, 'Peak' Flops and A24's 'Room' Strong in Limited Showing|author=Brad Brevet|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|date=2015-10-18|accessdate=2015-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151020003850/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4114&p=.htm|archive-date=2015-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該週的觀眾有60%是家庭，其次是25歲以下的59%，而男/女觀眾的比例則是50/50均分<ref name="GB"/>。

