== 續集 ==
{{main|怪物遊戲2：妖獸讚}}

2015年9月2日，據報導，續集正在規劃階段，而索尼則在為續集尋找編劇<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Goosebumps-2-Happening-Get-Details-80667.html | title=Goosebumps 2 Is Happening, Get The Details | publisher=Cinema Blend | date=2015-09-02 | accessdate=2015-09-03 | author=McKnight, Brent | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904160335/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Goosebumps-2-Happening-Get-Details-80667.html | archive-date=2015-09-04 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年1月17日，宣布上映日期為2018年1月26日<ref>{{cite web|last1=Evry|first1=Max|title=Goosebumps 2 Release Date Set By Sony Pictures|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/804137-goosebumps-2-release-date-set-by-sony-pictures|publisher=ComingSoon.net|accessdate=2017-01-18|date=2017-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120182333/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/804137-goosebumps-2-release-date-set-by-sony-pictures|archive-date=2017-01-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年2月6日，續集的上映日期推遲至2018年9月21日，取代《[[尖叫旅社3：怪獸假期|尖叫旅社3：怪獸假期]]》先前的檔期<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/811563-sony-pictures-2018-schedule#/slide/1|title=Sony Pictures 2018 Schedule Shifts Hotel Transylvania, Bad Boys, Goosebumps and More|date=2017-02-06|accessdate=2017-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207192652/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/811563-sony-pictures-2018-schedule#/slide/1|archive-date=2017-02-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年5月，宣布續集的片名為《Goosebumps: Horror Land》<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/849929-goosebumps-2-title-revealed-plus-promo-art-for-jumanji-grinch-and-more#/slide/2|title=Goosebumps 2 Title Revealed, Plus Promo Art for More!|date=2017-05-18|work=ComingSoon.net|access-date=2017-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518213645/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/849929-goosebumps-2-title-revealed-plus-promo-art-for-jumanji-grinch-and-more#/slide/2|archive-date=2017-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。傑克·布萊克也將回歸主演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3441519/jack-black-will-back-goosebumps-horrorland|title=Jack Black Will Be Back in 'Goosebumps: Horrorland'|date=2017-06-12|access-date=2019-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170919074125/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3441519/jack-black-will-back-goosebumps-horrorland|archive-date=2017-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年11月，羅布·李伯被聘來撰寫劇本<ref>{{cite web|last=Lang|first=Brent|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/sony-taps-rob-lieber-to-write-goosebumps-2-script-1202605455/amp/|title=''Sony'' Taps Rob Lieber To Write ''Goosebumps 2'' Script|date=2017-11-02|publisher=''Variety''|accessdate=2017-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204082658/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/sony-taps-rob-lieber-to-write-goosebumps-2-script-1202605455/amp/|archive-date=2017-12-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不久後，宣布{{link-en|亞里·桑多|Ari Sandel}}將取代羅勃·萊特曼擔任導演<ref>{{cite web|last=Lang|first=Brent|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/goosebumps-2-jack-black-1202637463/|title=Ari Sandel Will Direct ''Goosebumps 2''|date=2017-12-12|publisher=''Variety''|accessdate=2017-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171212185542/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/goosebumps-2-jack-black-1202637463/|archive-date=2017-12-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年12月，續集的上映日延期至2018年10月12日<ref>{{cite web |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |date=2017-12-28 |title=Sony Moves ‘Alpha’ To Fall, Bumps ‘Goosebumps 2’ To October |url=http://deadline.com/2017/12/jack-black-goosebumps-2-alpha-new-release-dates-1202233292/ |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2017-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180728092932/http://deadline.com/2017/12/jack-black-goosebumps-2-alpha-new-release-dates-1202233292/ |archive-date=2018-07-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

